SET ECHO OFF
* ============================================================
* ORDER_ITERATOR_REGRESSION_001.DTS
*
* Purpose:
*   Standard regression for ordered-iteration commands.
*
* Scope:
*   - SMARTLIST natural / INX / CNX / CDX
*   - ASC / DESC behavior
*   - TOP consistency under active order
*   - SCHEMAS save/load order restoration
*
* Notes:
*   - Assumes STUDENTS exists
*   - Assumes STUDENTS has:
*       students.inx
*       students.cnx
*       students.cdx
*     with tag/order LNAME available
* ============================================================

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO ORDER ITERATOR REGRESSION 001
ECHO ============================================================

SCHEMAS CLOSE
SCHEMAS OPEN DBF

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 1: Natural order baseline ---
SELECT STUDENTS
SET ORDER TO 0
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 2: INX baseline ---
SET INDEX TO STUDENTS.inx
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 3: CNX ascending ---
SET INDEX TO STUDENTS.cnx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 4: CNX descending ---
DESCEND
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 5: CNX TOP consistency ---
ASCEND
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 6: CDX ascending ---
SET INDEX TO STUDENTS.cdx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
ASCEND
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 7: CDX descending ---
DESCEND
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 8: CDX TOP consistency ---
ASCEND
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 9: Workspace save/load with active CDX tag ---
SCHEMAS SAVE idx_smoke
SCHEMAS CLOSE
SCHEMAS LOAD idx_smoke
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 10: Workspace save/load with relations + order ---
SET RELATIONS CLEAR ALL
SET RELATIONS ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
SET RELATIONS ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
REL REFRESH
REL LIST ALL
SCHEMAS SAVE rel_idx_smoke
SCHEMAS CLOSE
SCHEMAS LOAD rel_idx_smoke
AREA
REL LIST ALL
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO --- Section 11: Return to natural order ---
SET ORDER TO 0
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO.
ECHO ============================================================
ECHO ORDER ITERATOR REGRESSION COMPLETE
ECHO ============================================================
